#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:2
msgid "Customize Type Conversion Rules"
msgstr "自定义类型转换规则"

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:4
msgid ""
"Sometimes the default auto-conversion tools provided by asbind20 are not "
"enough for handling special user-defined types, it requires user to provide "
"rules for translating them between C++ and AngelScript."
msgstr ""
"有时 asbind20 提供的默认自动转换工具不足以处理特殊的用户定义类型，这需要用户"
"提供在 C++ 和 AngelScript 之间转换它们的规则。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:8
msgid "Example for ``std::byte``"
msgstr "``std::byte`` 的示例"

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:10
msgid ""
"The ``std::byte`` is defined using ``enum class byte : unsigned char {};``. "
"However, the default logic of type translator will convert enumerations to "
"``int`` because all underlying type of ``enum`` in AngelScript is ``int`` by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"``std::byte`` 使用 ``enum class byte : unsigned char {};`` 定义。但是，类型转"
"换器的默认逻辑会将枚举转换为 ``int``，因为在 AngelScript 中所有 ``enum`` 的底"
"层类型默认都是 ``int``。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:15
msgid ""
"For enumerations with custom underlying types, asbind20 provides a utility "
"for quickly implementing the traits."
msgstr ""
"对于具有自定义底层类型的枚举，asbind20 提供了一个用于快速实现类型特征的实用程"
"序。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:20
msgid "Example usage:"
msgstr "使用示例："

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:30
msgid ""
"Here is detailed example for how to make ``std::byte`` be treated as "
"``uint8`` by asbind20. You can apply this logic to the type that you want to "
"have customized rules."
msgstr ""
"以下是一个详细示例，展示了如何让 asbind20 将 ``std::byte`` 视为 ``uint8``。您"
"可以将此逻辑应用于您希望自定义规则的类型。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:63
msgid ""
"The above conversion rule is already defined in ``asbind20/type_traits.hpp``."
msgstr "上述转换规则已在 ``asbind20/type_traits.hpp`` 中定义。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/custom_conv_rule.rst:66
msgid "Reference of Conversion Rules Provided by asbind20"
msgstr "asbind20 提供的转换规则参考"
